                specialize in creating intuitive and user-centered interfaces
                for a wide range of digital products and experiences.
            </p>
        </div>
    </Section>
    <Section>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <h2>My past work experience</h2>
            <div>
                {
                    EXPERIENCE.map((exp) => {
                        return (
